840
00:41:12,960 --> 00:41:13,560
Note this:

841
00:41:14,020 --> 00:41:16,010
no obvious foreign objects
in the deceased's chest,

842
00:41:16,010 --> 00:41:18,010
abdomen, nasal cavity, or trachea.

843
00:41:19,670 --> 00:41:21,440
The liver and kidneys show
no signs of toxins.

844
00:41:21,440 --> 00:41:22,880
However, the victim had consumed
a large amount of alcohol

845
00:41:22,880 --> 00:41:24,280
prior to being abducted.

846
00:41:25,240 --> 00:41:26,440
The heart shows no damage

847
00:41:26,440 --> 00:41:27,570
but is pale in color,

848
00:41:27,920 --> 00:41:30,190
consistent with syncope
caused by extreme pain,

849
00:41:30,190 --> 00:41:33,280
followed by cardiac failure
due to insufficient blood flow.

850
00:41:33,280 --> 00:41:35,540
Indeed, he was tortured to death in pain.

851
00:41:50,050 --> 00:41:50,650
Note this:

852
00:41:50,960 --> 00:41:53,450
food remnants are still present
in the stomach.

853
00:41:53,450 --> 00:41:54,380
The last meal

854
00:41:54,400 --> 00:41:55,530
was about four hours

855
00:41:55,550 --> 00:41:56,550
before death.

856
00:41:57,070 --> 00:41:58,960
Judging by the food remnants,

857
00:41:59,150 --> 00:42:00,750
the last meal included crab.

858
00:42:00,770 --> 00:42:02,230
Crab's hard to come by this season,

859
00:42:02,230 --> 00:42:03,340
but some upscale restaurants

860
00:42:03,340 --> 00:42:05,030
reserve it for wealthy families.

861
00:42:05,030 --> 00:42:07,070
Shall we search all the restaurants
in the city?

862
00:42:07,070 --> 00:42:07,630
We can't.

863
00:42:08,190 --> 00:42:09,630
His Majesty has specifically instructed

864
00:42:09,630 --> 00:42:11,890
that this matter concerns
the capital's security,

865
00:42:11,890 --> 00:42:13,320
and we must not disturb the citizens

866
00:42:13,320 --> 00:42:14,280
or incite panic.

867
00:42:17,840 --> 00:42:20,230
