indicating that the location
where the killer skinned the victim

872
00:42:26,490 --> 00:42:29,310
is likely close to where the body was
dumped and where the kidnapping occurred.

873
00:42:29,310 --> 00:42:30,570
And that alley where the body was dumped

874
00:42:30,570 --> 00:42:32,410
has a restaurant in front
and Fengqi House behind.

875
00:42:32,410 --> 00:42:33,990
That restaurant specializes in
stir-fried crab,

876
00:42:33,990 --> 00:42:35,070
whereas Fengqi House

877
00:42:35,070 --> 00:42:36,800
is famous for its steamed crab.

878
00:42:38,210 --> 00:42:40,870
