886
00:43:08,920 --> 00:43:09,840
Constable Zhan!

887
00:43:09,840 --> 00:43:10,960
Go to Fengqi House immediately

888
00:43:10,960 --> 00:43:12,240
and check which customers ordered

889
00:43:12,240 --> 00:43:13,960
steamed crab during the afternoon

890
00:43:13,960 --> 00:43:15,440
and evening of the day of the incident.

891
00:43:15,440 --> 00:43:15,970
Yes, sir.

892
00:43:21,320 --> 00:43:23,840
Master Wan, your deduction is
precise and thorough,

893
00:43:23,840 --> 00:43:25,780
which reminds me of someone.

894
00:43:30,570 --> 00:43:31,290
Who?

895
00:43:32,800 --> 00:43:34,260
None other than my mentor,

896
00:43:34,660 --> 00:43:36,820
the late Lord Shen Yi.

897
00:43:37,710 --> 00:43:40,150
The solemnity in your expression
during the autopsy

898
00:43:40,150 --> 00:43:41,400
mirrors that of

899
00:43:41,400 --> 00:43:42,650
my mentor's demeanor

900
00:43:42,680 --> 00:43:43,800
during autopsies.

901
00:43:49,480 --> 00:43:50,450
I used to believe

902
00:43:50,670 --> 00:43:53,200
Master Wan's autopsy skills were
unmatched.

903
00:43:53,920 --> 00:43:55,550
If Lord Shen were still alive,

904
00:43:55,550 --> 00:43:58,280
perhaps they could have learned from
each other.

905
00:43:59,190 --> 00:44:00,520
I've spoken out of turn.

906
00:44:00,920 --> 00:44:03,250
His Majesty is waiting for my report.

907
00:44:03,590 --> 00:44:04,720
I must take my leave.

908
00:44:08,300 --> 00:44:09,760
Get there safely, Lord Li.

909
00:44:20,200 --> 00:44:22,110
Let's go to
the Ministry of Justice prison.

910
00:44:22,110 --> 00:44:22,960
Why the rush?

911
00:44:23,840 --> 00:44:26,300
Since he said I resemble
Lord Shen somewhat,

912
00:44:26,630 --> 00:44:27,470
I must quickly

913
00:44:27,470 --> 00:44:29,580
resolve the suspicious case he left behind

914
00:44:29,580 --> 00:44:31,150
to live up to this honor.

